Meteor Men (01 - 05) (2014) (digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)


On a summer night, Alden Baylor sits in a field watching the largest meteor shower in human history. What begins as teenage adventure becomes something more--the celestial event brings travelers who will change the world completely, and Alden discovers a connection to one of them. From writer Jeff Parker (AQUAMAN, HULK), artist Sandy Jarrell (BATMAN 66), and colorist Kevin Volo comes this story of adolescence, friendship, and hard decisions.
